*'''Master Lawyer''': Hogarth established [[Hogarth, Chao & Benowitz|her law firm]] and specializes in criminal law, never losing a case. She has the ability to analyze how a jury will think and manipulate circumstances to her favor, exemplified by when she used [[Trish Walker]] to change public opinion on the possible existence of mind controllers. When focused, Hogarth can negotiate to make other litigators settle out of court, thus continuing her reputed winning streak. However, since that is not her specialty, she allowed [[Desmond Tobey]] to handle her divorce proceedings. Nevertheless, Hogarth continued to work cases to her own benefit, including lessening [[Shane Ryback]]'s sentencing and allowing him freedom from prison.
