*'''{{WPS|Smith & Wesson Model 60}}''': Hogarth bought this revolver from [[Turk Barrett]] in order to enact her revenge against [[Shane Ryback]] and [[Inez Green]]. Hogarth gave the gun to Green, and told her lies about how Ryback had also conned her by flattering other women. Moments later, Green killed Ryback with the gun, and Hogarth anonymously reported the crime to the police. Hogarth owned another revolver and took it when [[Trish Walker]] took [[Kith Lyonne]] as a hostage while negotiating with her. She ended up shooting [[Jessica Jones]] in the leg to prevent her from following them, in order to make Walker set Lyonne free.

