==Trivia==
*In the comics, '''Jerry Hogarth''' is a businessman who worked with [[Wendell Rand]] and became a trusted ally of his son, [[Danny Rand]].
*Hogarth is the first lesbian character in the [[Marvel Cinematic Universe]].

==Behind the Scenes==
*[[Stefanie Flores]] and [[Dejay Roestenberg]] were stunt doubles for [[Carrie-Anne Moss]] in the role of Jeri Hogarth.

